title: Santa Monica Chapter Holistic Chamber Of Commerce Network Meeting!
desc: The Santa Monica Chapter vision is to create community. Come together to develop friendships and alliances, inspire one another and have fun growing our businesses. Be a community of support to one another by sharing our expertise and referrals.?Prosperity is for everyone; we need to claim it and create it! ?The way to success is by helping other people get what they want. Lets share in the blessings and have some fun!? December Meeting: We're having a Holiday Party and Visioning Success for 2016!?  All are welcome come and celebrate with us!
